{"tid":2192842,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"憶做衝衝子「最能夠做返自己」","createTime":"2020-09-07T11:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T15:13:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ef27af1690f44a467cc7cd8b47db3397057ca740","tid":2192842,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:25:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/BDZU3XSNJFFJZNQDTISWORXIPA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FBDZU3XSNJFFJZNQDTISWORXIPA%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=1a5c44a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200907%2FBDZU3XSNJFFJZNQDTISWORXIPA%2F&h=d22d5b35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200907/BDZU3XSNJFFJZNQDTISWORXIPA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n憶做衝衝子「最能夠做返自己」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2mIKPXfz9GutqyLKnAqVdWJgQsQ=/2061x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/22KFV4F2T5A7LDY4GXNOGXWE6I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2mIKPXfz9GutqyLKnAqVdWJgQsQ%3D%2F2061x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F22KFV4F2T5A7LDY4GXNOGXWE6I.jpg&h=d02b4645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■去年反送中抗爭爆發，鄭文傑曾全副武裝站在前線包圍警察總部。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。惟有與香港手足們站在前線抗爭，他才感覺做回真正的自己：「戴上頭盔向前衝嗰一刻，係我做咗廿幾年人，最能夠做返我自己、最能夠實踐自我價值嘅時候！」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：中共魔爪伸到英國  鄭文傑設手足避風驛<br />\n<br />\n部份人或有疑問，到底鄭文傑是否受到中共禁錮虐待後才轉黃？。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n憤慨難平的他，開始關注中國的民主及人權狀況，每年也會出席六四集會，他笑說其「大中華膠」的稱號亦因此而來，「當時覺得香港仲有自由，要幫內地嘅人爭取民主，估唔到今時今日，連自己嘅自由都保唔住」。<br />\n<br />\n之後他在台灣讀大學，主修政治與國際關係，以香港人的角度，研究一國兩制及兩岸關係。雨傘運動時，他因身在台灣，而未能參與，但當時視線從未離開香港。到了反送中運動，他終於可以親身參與。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為二百萬人上街自豪<br />\n<br />\n去年6月，當時他仍是英國駐港領事館職員，正在英國出差，在新聞看到200萬人走上街頭，他感到非常激動：「作為英國政府公務員，係好忌諱，唔應該發表政治諗法，但當時真係按捺唔住我嘅激動，喺社交網站公開咁寫，香港人我以你哋為驕傲！」<br />\n<br />\n他更迫不及待提早完結英國行程回港，特地請假，第一次全副武裝，與抗爭者並肩站在前線包圍警察總部。戴上頭盔向前衝那一刻，他表示從未感到如此滿足：「終於感覺到我可以實踐自己嘅價值，可以做返我自己！」<br />\n<br />\n鄭文傑曾經跟許多香港人一樣，背負沉重包袱，包括家人和工作，只能在各種局限中，盡力嘗試在這場運動作出一點貢獻，就像一顆顆小螺絲釘。但他深信若果大家都能堅持信念，兄弟爬山，每人做一點點，終有一天能改變強權巨輪，將香港人的理想，變為現實。"},{"pid":"6f626e16221cdacaa5556eca61d1db86ca91b9ca","tid":2192842,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:27:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0060cbc05d550cfa7148539f83e7ac53e7739099","tid":2192842,"uid":321255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:32:06.000Z","msg":"天佑港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n天佑手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日做嘅嘢係共產黨逼出黎嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好人好者<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都打下機聽下歌夠鐘起身屌下閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5e69d6ef8ebb4a9d8e40b6d9d4a77cda5ae82b","tid":2192842,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:06:18.000Z","msg":"最慘既係佢以前成日要同支那人打交道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肯定好撚辛苦"},{"pid":"40e71734dd06535c521bb5a8b37c0f262f72bd52","tid":2192842,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T15:13:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}